Account Insights Embedded Dashboard

The Account Insights Embedded Dashboard allows you to understand your account's opportunities, quotes, and orders. The dashboard provides the following sections:

Understand Your Account Opportunities
Understand Your Account Quotes
Understand Your Account Orders

Each section includes a description of what can be seen in that section and key performance indicators (KPIs) used to calculate certain metrics.

The KPI calculations for each section are also listed, including formulas and counts.
title: Embedding and Customizing Account Insights Dashboard in Salesforce
